data.description: Inviting home located in the City of Euclid! This is not your typical bungalow, cape-cod, colonial home found in the area. This spacious split-level home, on a corner lot, with a sizable backyard offers updates that every new homeowner will appreciate. Updates include 2021 siding, 2020 roofing, 2019 hot water tank, 2015 sump pump and waterproofing, 2014 windows, and electrical panel. Catch a tee time, minutes away @ Briardale Greens Golf Course, or Friday night lights @ the state-of-the-art stadium at Euclid High School! The home is also near the I-90 interstate, restaurants, shopping, and Downtown Cleveland.
